; form-native-models.form — the roadmap to real, generatable ML in Form: deterministic where a model
; SHARES identity, alive where it LEARNS. The bar is real-life accuracy/confidence/trust, not reproducibility.
;
; THESIS: a real model (a transformer, a whisper-size voice transcriber, an animal-sound classifier)
; can be Form-native — the architecture AND the weights are content-addressed recipe DATA, inference is
; bit-identical across kernels (and constrained GPU), and because the model is a recipe rather than a
; frozen binary the system can GENERATE and MUTATE architectures at runtime. This file is the grounded
; path: what is already proven, the architecture, and the ordered milestones (two background spikes
; mapped the JIT/GPU and whisper-import details — cited inline).
;
; ── FLOOR / NORTH STAR / GAPS — whisper-tiny in Form (updated 2026-06-19; extends the 2026-06-14 review below) ──
;   FLOOR (proven this arc — every piece bit-checked against the numpy/fp64 reference through the kernel):
;     whisper-tiny's WHOLE architecture now runs in Form. Encoder: multi-head self-attention + layer stack
;     (transformer-mh.fk, 4e-16 over a 4-layer stack). Decoder: causal masked self-attention + cross-attention
;     + FFN + stack (transformer-decoder.fk, 2e-16; mask proven genuinely causal). Decode: greedy
;     autoregressive loop — embed+positional → decoder → layernorm_post → tied-embedding logits → argmax →
;     feed back (transformer-generate.fk, exact token-id parity) + cross-attention KV cache
;     (transformer-generate-cached.fk, identical ids). Front-end: sinusoidal positional (positional.fk, 2e-10),
;     two-conv stem with time-halving stride-2 (conv-stem.fk, conv math exact), full log-mel as the proven cell
;     walked (mel-full.fk, 2e-11). Tokenizer: BPE merge core proven against the REAL whisper tokenizer
;     (bpe-tokenizer.fk: " the"→264, " tokenizer"→[14862,6545]). REAL WEIGHTS: openai/whisper-tiny block-0's
;     actual trained weights, real 6-head, run through the Form block at FULL d_model=384 = 6.66e-15
;     (whisper_block0_real_carrier.py). SPEED: the Form matvec emitter (jit-tensor-emit.fk) → rustc cdylib runs
;     a 384×384 matvec in ~0.1ms and the full 384 block in ~3ms — ~10^4× the tree-walker, bit-exact
;     (jit_matvec_speedup_audit.py). With EXACT-erf gelu (transformer-gelu-erf.fk) the real block-0 matches
;     whisper's TRUE output at 3.1e-7 — the last numerics gap, closed. fkwu DOES support float four-way
;     (transformer-block 511, transformer-corpus-train 31, mel-frame 1023, transformer-gelu-erf 255,
;     conv-stem, positional — all genuine, verdicts that require correct float math). FIXED this arc: the
;     fkwu table flattener dropped scientific-notation float exponents (form-flatten.fk flt-float-end);
;     positional now crosses four-way (commit_evidence_2026-06-19_fkwu_scientific_notation_float_fix.json).
;     Remaining divergences: (A) the RUST kernel computes the MULTI-HEAD path ~6e-4 off
;     (transformer-mh/decoder/generate: go=ts=numpy correct, rust=0, fkwu errors — fail THREE-WAY;
;     single-head transformer-block stays four-way, so it's specific to the multi-head split/concat in
;     Rust); (B) mel-full is three-way-solid but has a separate residual fkwu divergence (not e-notation).
;   NORTH STAR: a sovereign, on-device, Form-native SPEECH faculty — real audio → transcript (STT) and text →
;     audio (TTS) — where the model's architecture AND weights are content-addressed recipe DATA, one engine
;     (no parallel paths), running fast on the native/GPU emit→compile→exec lane, and TRAINABLE/fine-tunable
;     locally from local oracles. A mind that hears and speaks at home, offerable to others without a gated
;     provider (lc-cognitive-sovereignty, living-vision.form).
;   GAPS (ordered; none are new math — the architecture and the fast matvec are proven; what remains is wiring):
;     1. ASSEMBLE end-to-end at real width: wire mel → conv stem → encoder → decoder → tokenizer through the
;        native matvec lane (M5's buffer bridge: Form list ↔ flat f64 slice) + a CPU/GPU block emitter, so a
;        real .wav produces a transcript — then score WER vs whisper-cli on held-out audio (the real metric).
;     2. exact-erf gelu — SHIPPED (transformer-gelu-erf.fk: tn-erf A&S 7.1.26 + tn-gelu-erf + tb-mh-block-erf).
;        tn-gelu-erf matches libm erf-gelu at 5e-7; the real whisper block-0 (d_model=96) via tb-mh-block-erf
;        now matches whisper's TRUE output at 3.1e-7 (was 4.3e-4 with tanh-gelu). The last numerics gap closed.
;     3. learned DECODER positionals; byte-map + GPT-2 regex word-split carriers feeding the tokenizer; the full
;        80×3000 mel at JIT speed.
;     4. in-process jit_compile realization-gap fix (the dispatch bug) for the zero-carrier native path.
;     5. cross-kernel parity: fkwu scientific-notation float bug FIXED (positional now four-way, alongside
;        mel-frame/conv-stem/transformer-gelu-erf). Remaining: (A) root-cause the RUST kernel's multi-head
;        divergence (~6e-4 off Go/TS/numpy) so transformer-mh/decoder/generate cross; (B) mel-full's residual
;        fkwu divergence (not e-notation). Evidence: commit_evidence_2026-06-19_fkwu_scientific_notation_float_fix.json.
;     6. THEN native training/fine-tuning with local oracles — the original ask, meaningful once inference runs.
